{"segment":6,"line_start":129,"line_end":236,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_ao","text":"唐大公子真是用兵如神，选在端午前夕发动攻击，大风堂的人怎么会料得到？我相信上官堡攻陷的消息一定马上会传回来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":155,"line_end":157},{"speaker":"char_tang_ao","speaker_name":"唐傲","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"上官先生太夸奖了。有一件事我倒是对不起你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":159,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_ao","text":"哪一件？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":163,"line_end":163},{"speaker":"char_tang_ao","speaker_name":"唐傲","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"我不是跟你商量过，要在端午才发动攻击吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":165,"line_end":165},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_ao","text":"这算什么对不起？唐大公子高瞻远瞩，我是望尘莫及。说不定明天才攻打，损兵折将比今天会多得多。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":167,"line_end":169},{"speaker":"char_tang_ao","speaker_name":"唐傲","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"我就是这样想，才尽早进攻的，很抱歉没有先跟上官先生商量。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":171,"line_end":171},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_ao","text":"你太抬举我了。这种事，我可要听你指挥呐！","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":173,"line_end":173},{"speaker":"char_tang_ao","speaker_name":"唐傲","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"等一下上官堡攻陷的消息传来，上官先生知道我会做一件什么事吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":177,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_ao","text":"什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":181,"line_end":181},{"speaker":"char_tang_ao","speaker_name":"唐傲","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"我要把上官堡送给你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":183,"line_end":183},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_ao","text":"哦？真的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":185,"line_end":185},{"speaker":"char_tang_ao","speaker_name":"唐傲","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"真的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":187,"line_end":187},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_ao","text":"为什么？我才从那个地方来，你又要我回去那个地方？","tone":"激动","chapter":10,"line_start":189,"line_end":191},{"speaker":"char_tang_ao","speaker_name":"唐傲","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"上官先生别误会。大风堂的上官堡，和唐家的上官堡，地位是只有过之的。","tone":"淡然","chapter":10,"line_start":193,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_tang_ao","speaker_name":"唐傲","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"我准备把作战的最前线放在上官堡，请上官先生去那里，就是要主持整个重要决战的决策。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":199,"line_end":200},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_ao","text":"来，我敬你一杯，老夫投靠唐家堡，等的就是这一天，能够直接参与消灭大风堂的行动。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":10,"line_start":203,"line_end":204},{"speaker":"char_lao_zu_zong","speaker_name":"老祖宗","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"你为什么这么恨大风堂？你来这里，我都没有问过你这个问题。为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":207,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_lao_zu_zong","text":"哼！当年建立大风堂的基业，谁的功劳最大？你知道吗？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":10,"line_start":211,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_tang_que","speaker_name":"唐缺","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"当然是上官先生。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":215,"line_end":215},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_que","text":"可不是，但是，为什么我的地位竟然跟赵简和司空晓风一样？当年多少生死大战，都是我和常主一起参与的，赵简和司空晓风只不过有镇守之功而已，凭什么跟我平起平坐？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":10,"line_start":217,"line_end":220},{"speaker":"char_tang_que","speaker_name":"唐缺","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"是呀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":223,"line_end":223},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_ren","speaker_name":"上官刃","listener":"char_tang_que","text":"我已经对他们忍受了很久！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":10,"line_start":225,"line_end":226},{"speaker":"char_lao_zu_zong","speaker_name":"老祖宗","listener":"char_shang_guan_ren","text":"恭喜你了！","tone":"微笑","chapter":10,"line_start":231,"line_end":232}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_tang_ao","name":"唐傲","alias":"唐大公子","identity":"唐家堡大公子，消灭大风堂行动总指挥","faction":"faction_tang_jia_bao","role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"唐家堡大公子，用兵狡诈，骗赵无忌端午进攻实则提前攻打，同时攻击大风堂三个据点","personality":{"traits":["狡猾多疑","心狠手辣","自负骄傲","善于权谋","观察入微"],"speech_style":"礼貌中暗藏锋芒","temperament":"深沉冷静"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_shang_guan_ren","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"利用与试探"},{"target":"char_zhao_wu_ji","type":"宿敌","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"骗约已破，血仇加深"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":136,"line_end":139,"text":"唐傲很仔细的观察上官刃的笑容。他希望从上官刃的笑容里，看出他是真的高兴，还是虚假的应酬。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":159,"line_end":160,"text":"\"上官先生太夸奖了。有一件事我倒是对不起你。\""},{"chapter":10,"line_start":177,"line_end":178,"text":"\"等一下上官堡攻陷的消息传来，上官先生知道我会做一件什么事吗？\""},{"chapter":10,"line_start":199,"line_end":200,"text":"\"我准备把作战的最前线放在上官堡，请上官先生去那里，就是要主持整个重要决战的决策。\""}]},{"id":"char_shang_guan_ren","name":"上官刃","alias":"上官先生","identity":"原大风堂创始人之一，现投靠唐家堡","faction":"faction_tang_jia_bao","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"大风堂创始人之一，因不满地位与赵简司空晓风平起平坐而投靠唐家堡，面笑心悲","personality":{"traits":["老谋深算","善于伪装","骄傲自负","心有不甘","隐忍"],"speech_style":"谦恭中藏锋芒","temperament":"表里不一"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_tang_ao","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"互相试探利用"},{"target":"char_zhao_jian","type":"宿敌","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"旧怨——地位之争"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":141,"line_end":143,"text":"上官刃虽然不知道唐十七已经被杀，但他却对自己的演戏天才充满信心。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":145,"line_end":147,"text":"其实他的内心正感到无限感伤。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":217,"line_end":220,"text":"\"可不是，但是，为什么我的地位竟然跟赵简和司空晓风一样？当年多少生死大战，都是我和常主一起参与的，赵简和司空晓风只不过有镇守之功而已，凭什么跟我平起平坐？\""},{"chapter":10,"line_start":225,"line_end":226,"text":"\"我已经对他们忍受了很久！\""}]},{"id":"char_tang_que","name":"唐缺","alias":null,"identity":"唐家堡成员","faction":"faction_tang_jia_bao","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"唐家堡成员，陪宴时随口附和上官刃","personality":{"traits":["善于应和","圆滑"],"speech_style":"附和讨好","temperament":"圆滑世故"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":131,"line_end":132,"text":"桌上只有四个人：唐傲、唐缺、老祖宗和上官刃。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":215,"line_end":216,"text":"\"当然是上官先生。\""},{"chapter":10,"line_start":223,"line_end":224,"text":"\"是呀。\""}]},{"id":"char_lao_zu_zong","name":"老祖宗","alias":null,"identity":"唐家堡长辈或重要人物","faction":"faction_tang_jia_bao","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"唐家堡重要人物，参与宴饮并询问上官刃为何恨大风堂","personality":{"traits":["深沉","警觉","善于提问"],"speech_style":"直接有力","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":131,"line_end":132,"text":"桌上只有四个人：唐傲、唐缺、老祖宗和上官刃。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":207,"line_end":208,"text":"\"你为什么这么恨大风堂？你来这里，我都没有问过你这个问题。为什么？\""},{"chapter":10,"line_start":231,"line_end":232,"text":"老祖宗笑着，把纸条交给上官刃，道：\"恭喜你了！\""}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_tang_jia_bao","name":"唐家堡","type":"家族","location":"唐家堡","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"以暗器和毒药闻名的武林世家，正在全面进攻大风堂","source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":129,"line_end":131,"text":"丰盛的菜，珍藏的酒，愉快的一道晚宴正在唐家贵宾厅举行。桌上只有四个人：唐傲、唐缺、老祖宗和上官刃。"}]}],"locations":[{"id":"loc_tang_jia_bao","name":"唐家堡","region":"唐家堡领地","one_line":"唐家堡大本营，唐家贵宾厅正在进行庆功宴","source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":129,"line_end":130,"text":"丰盛的菜，珍藏的酒，愉快的一道晚宴正在唐家贵宾厅举行。"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":7,"line_start":237,"line_end":379,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"你应该高兴才对。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":251,"line_end":251},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"我知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":253,"line_end":253},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"那你为什么愁眉不展？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":255,"line_end":255},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"因为我看到你的表情，忍不住也伤感。","tone":"温柔","chapter":10,"line_start":257,"line_end":257},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"你人不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":263,"line_end":263},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"我人是很好的。而且，我还有更好的事要做。","tone":"微笑","chapter":10,"line_start":265,"line_end":265},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":267,"line_end":267},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"我要带你离开这里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":269,"line_end":269},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"真的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":271,"line_end":271},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"真的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":273,"line_end":273},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"你不怕危险？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":275,"line_end":275},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"我什么也不怕。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":277,"line_end":277},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"今晚？会不会太仓促？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":283,"line_end":283},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"不会。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":285,"line_end":285},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":287,"line_end":287},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"因为我已经计划了一整天了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":289,"line_end":289},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":291,"line_end":291},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"从昨天晚上开始，我都在想着你的事。我想，为了表示我对你的喜爱程度，我必须有所抉择。","tone":"温柔","chapter":10,"line_start":293,"line_end":295},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"所以我决定帮你逃走。你应该知道，我私自带你逃走，是什么样的大罪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":301,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"我知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":305,"line_end":305},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"我知道。假如他们不杀我，我一辈子都会记得你。","tone":"感动","chapter":10,"line_start":309,"line_end":309},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"假如逃得成，我这一辈子也会很痛苦。我会成为唐家的通辑犯。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":311,"line_end":311},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"我很感激你。不过，有没有什么方法，可以不让唐家堡的人，知道是你协助我逃跑的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":313,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"没有。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":317,"line_end":317},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"你想过吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":319,"line_end":319},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"想过，唐家上上下下的人都知道我对你的痴迷程度。你走了，我怎么会不知道？","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":321,"line_end":323},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"那你还是要带我走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":325,"line_end":325},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":327,"line_end":327},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"我不能向你保证以后的事。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":329,"line_end":329},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"我知道。我是个欲望很低的人。我只要时常看到你，就心满意足，别的什么也不求了。","tone":"温柔","chapter":10,"line_start":331,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"你又怎么了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":343,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"我想起无忌。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":10,"line_start":347,"line_end":347},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"别乱想，赶快把饭吃完，好好休息一下，晚上要熬夜逃走。","tone":"严肃","chapter":10,"line_start":355,"line_end":356},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"我们什么时候走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":359,"line_end":359},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"子夜过后。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":361,"line_end":361},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"为什么选在这个时候？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":363,"line_end":363},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"因为子时附近，是人最沉睡的时候，精神最不振，熬过了这段时间，精神又恢复过来，人就变得警觉性特别高。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":365,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"唐家堡的人也是这样吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":369,"line_end":369},{"speaker":"char_tang_hua","speaker_name":"唐花","listener":"char_wei_feng_niang","text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":371,"line_end":371},{"speaker":"char_wei_feng_niang","speaker_name":"卫凤娘","listener":"char_tang_hua","text":"好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":379,"line_end":379}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_wei_feng_niang","name":"卫凤娘","alias":"凤娘","identity":"赵无忌的恋人，被囚于唐家堡","faction":"faction_da_feng_tang","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"赵无忌的恋人，被囚于唐家堡，对大风堂惨剧感伤不已，被唐花以白玉雕龙计划欺骗","personality":{"traits":["纯真善良","情感丰富","易感动","忠诚于无忌","柔弱"],"speech_style":"温婉真挚","temperament":"敏感多愁"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_zhao_wu_ji","type":"恋人","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"深爱思念"},{"target":"char_tang_hua","type":"主仆","intensity":30,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"被欺骗利用"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":239,"line_end":239,"text":"卫凤娘。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":249,"line_end":250,"text":"但当他看到卫凤娘那充满感伤的容颜时，脸上居然也露出感伤的神情来。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":297,"line_end":298,"text":"卫风娘感动得差点快掉眼泪了。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":337,"line_end":338,"text":"她忽然想起了无忌。她何尝不是跟眼前的唐花一样？只想时常看到无忌，别的也不求什么。"}]},{"id":"char_tang_hua","name":"唐花","alias":null,"identity":"唐家堡成员，白玉雕龙计划执行者","faction":"faction_tang_jia_bao","role":"npc","archetype":"assassin","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"奉命执行白玉雕龙计划，假装对卫凤娘痴迷，计划带她逃离唐家堡以获取信任","personality":{"traits":["虚伪狡诈","冷静残酷","善于演戏","会内疚但转瞬即逝","城府深"],"speech_style":"温柔多情，实则算计","temperament":"外热内冷"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_wei_feng_niang","type":"主仆","intensity":20,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"利用欺骗"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":241,"line_end":242,"text":"唐花是奉命执行白玉雕龙计划的人，白玉雕龙计划的第一步，就是先要获得卫凤娘的信任。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":299,"line_end":300,"text":"唐花看在眼里，知道自己的话已经打动她的心。他更知道，以卫凤娘的个性，要推动白玉雕龙的计划，真是轻而易举的事。"},{"chapter":10,"line_start":351,"line_end":353,"text":"欺骗这么纯真的一个女子，唐花心中居然有一丝隐隐然的轻微内疚。然而这份轻微的内疚只是一闪而过，他很快的又变回冷静残酷的唐家人面貌。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_bai_yu_diao_long","name":"白玉雕龙","type":"special","owner":null,"one_line":"唐家堡的计划名称，第一步是获取卫凤娘的信任","description":"唐家堡针对大风堂制定的秘密计划，由唐花执行，第一步是通过假装痴迷获取卫凤娘的信任，进而利用她达到某种目的","effects":[],"origin":"唐家堡","rarity":"稀世珍品","related_characters":["char_tang_hua","char_wei_feng_niang"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":241,"line_end":241,"text":"白玉雕龙计划的第一步，就是先要获得卫凤娘的信任。"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
